<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3189] Stagger Major Compactions</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3189</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For pre-split regions, we can get into a case where the oldest HFile in a Store is pretty large and will not encounter a compaction within the 24hr major compact window.  If that&apos;s the case, we don&apos;t want multiple multi-GB major compactions being triggered at the same time.  Add ability to stagger the major compaction expiration window.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12478938">HBASE-3189</key>
            <summary>Stagger Major Compactions</summary>
